# The `Symbol` Struct Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

The purpose of this struct is to only expose the symbol information that an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/lto/lto">LTO</a> client should need in order to do symbol resolution. <a href="#details">More...</a>
